commit message:
UnicodeTranscript: introduce convenience function for width of char in array

There are several places in the code where we're doing something like
this:

char[] line;
if (Character.isHighSurrogate(line[i])) {
UnicodeTranscript.charWidth(line[i], line[i+1]);
} else {
UnicodeTranscript.charWidth(line[i]);
}

Add a convenience function to aid readability.
